# Ollama is local and keyless — this recipe needs NO API key and no .env file.
# The Bir "server" in this lesson is a fake the script starts ITSELF on
# 127.0.0.1 with an ephemeral port; nothing to configure, nothing leaves your
# machine.
#
# Optional: point at a non-default Ollama server (the ollama client reads this
# natively). Leave unset to use the local default (http://localhost:11434).
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://localhost:11434
